HOMEPAGE = http://www.pocoo.org/projects/markupsafe/
COMMENT  = MarkupSafe is a library for Python that implements a unicode string that is aware of HTML escaping rules and can be used to implement automatic string escaping. It is used by Jinja 2, the Mako templating engine, the Pylons web framework and many more.
